====================
=  README for ex2  =
====================
==================
=  Description:  =
==================
this exercise includes different mathematical functions, that use:
calling other functions; getting parameters and returning different types;
user's input; nested if, and more.
======================
=  Special Comments  =
======================
the chosen edge cases on test_largest_and_smallest function:
1,3,3 - two of the three are equal and maximal numbers
6,-6,6 - two of the three are equal and minimal numbers
0,0,0 - three equal numbers
19.7, 17,17.9 - using both int and float types numbers
17,17.9,19.7 - same as the previous numbers, in a different order